Package: SuSiEIRLS
Type: Package
Title: SuSiE for non-Gaussian outcomes via IRLS
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: Implements Sum of Single Effects (SuSiE) fine-mapping for
    generalized linear, ordered-categorical, and Cox proportional-hazards
    outcomes using IRLS or score-based sufficient statistics with penalized
    refitting.
